    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Cracca schiedeana are respiratory problems, such as bronchitis, which are treated with its decoction to expel mucus and reduce inflammation. Cracca schiedeana's anti-inflammatory properties also alleviate gastrointestinal issues, including gastritis, by decreasing inflammation in the stomach lining. Additionally, the plant's antispasmodic properties help to calm menstrual cramps and other spasmodic conditions, such as asthma. Its antioxidant and antimicrobial properties make it effective in treating skin conditions like eczema, which is characterized by redness and itching. Furthermore, Cracca schiedeana's antiseptic properties help to heal wounds and ulcers by inhibiting the growth of bacteria and promoting tissue repair.",
